Global FRP Repair Kit Market Insights
FRP Repair Kit Market size was valued at USD 1.2 Billion in 2022 and is projected to reach USD 2.5 Billion by 2030, growing at a CAGR of 8.6% from 2024 to 2030.

FRP Repair Kit Market Overview
The global FRP (Fiberglass Reinforced Plastic) repair kit market is poised for significant growth, reaching a market value of approximately USD 1.5 billion by 2025. The increasing adoption of FRP materials in various industries, including construction, automotive, and marine, has been a major factor driving the market. With growing demand for durable and cost-effective repair solutions, FRP repair kits are becoming essential tools for maintaining and extending the life of FRP structures. The market is also benefiting from technological advancements and innovations in the repair materials themselves.

